@@@ Rviz Visual Tools Setup
@@@ VincentChan
@@@ 26th-May 2020

Reference : https://github.com/PickNikRobotics/rviz_visual_tools

1) Install rviz visual tools
   $ cd catkin_ws/src
   $ sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-rviz-visual-tools

2) Build from source 
   $ cd catkin_Ws
   $ rosdep install --from-paths src --ignore-src --rosdistro melodic
   $ catkin_make

3) Run demo for testing
   $ roslaunch rviz_visual_tools demo_rviz.launch
   $ roslaunch rviz_visual_tools demo.launch

